name: Princess sister of Dress-up Girl sweet salon game
name_original: Princess sister of Dress-up Girl sweet salon game
description:
If You love Princess. She'll back!! Everyone loves dress up games.. But they get boring. This is not your usual dress up game.

Princess dress-up game with high fashion dresses!
The combinations allow for seemingly endless fun!

Features:
- 8 Princess Girls Character
- 14 Magic
- 15 Dresses
- 20 Hair
- 15 symbol
- 19 pants
- 6 backgrounds settings
- that's over 4,500,000 combinations!
- Hours of entertainment
